Hello,

My name is Michael, founder of NuHorizon SD LLC, your host, and welcome to my Turo profile! (Co-hosted by Paola)

I aim to provide an excellent car rental experience. 🫡

🌟I prioritize clear and prompt communication with my renters, ensuring that their questions and concerns are addressed promptly. 🌟

🌟I strive to make the rental process as convenient as possible, offering flexible pick-up and drop-off options and providing detailed instructions to ensure a smooth experience.🌟

🌟 I maintain the highest standards of cleanliness and upkeep for my vehicles, ensuring that each rental is a comfortable and enjoyable experience for the customers.🌟

Furthermore, I am a responsible and trustworthy person who prioritizes integrity and honesty in all aspects of life. I am also reliable and always follow through on my commitments. Thank you for reading my bio! 🫶

My goal is to provide the best client experience with my fleet of high end cars. You'll find in my many reviews that I am very responsive, accessible and flexible with my guests; message or call me anytime. Personally I am passionate about cars and I love chatting with my guest about their cars and driving experience.

I offer 24/7 airport delivery, long-term, and repeat customer discounts.

ATTENTION RENTER...
I take great pride in keeping my cars cleaned and SANITIZED. To prevent the spread of germs during this pandemic every car is sanitized and cleaned thoroughly with anti-bacterial before and after each trip. Rest assured you are driving the world's cleanest germ free rental car on the market!

Elevate Ventures Inc. thanks you for visiting one of our three locations.

We started with one car and worked our way up to a fleet 🚙🚗🚙. We pride ourselves on offering an elevated experience within the Turo Platform.

About the founders of Elevate Ventures: It was started by two partners with a background in investments 📉. With over six years of experience, they recognized that consumers were not offered enough and decided to rent cars out with a conscious model, aiming to make the car-sharing experience pleasant.

Together, it takes us all to create a great hospitality experience. 😊

We are here to make your car rental experience at its best. No more endless papework or waiting in line

Hello!
I am 36 year old single mom of 3 amazing kids. Born and raised in beautiful San Diego. I've been in the car business for 7 years, but just started in the car rental industry a year ago. 

Thank you every single one of you for supporting my small business.  Your help has given me the opportunity to provide for my kids.  I now have the time to raise and spend quality time with them. This wouldn't be possible without your support.

From the bottom of my heart,  thank you,  thank you,  thank you 🙏
